{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781423297309,"sessionID":"ses_13aef63ccffel7tpaI1Dzxs3uq","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_5a08037d70a94d06b5f72f65","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"rg -n \"In Progress\" .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/spec.md 2>/dev/null | head -5","description":"Verify F001 still holds","workdir":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public"},"output":"127:| 000 | `000-release-cleanup/` | Outward and governance surface alignment for release: public README, skill docs, feature catalog, manual playbook, MCP/CLI stress, commands, agents, AGENTS.md | In Progress |\n128:| 001 | `001-research-and-doctrine/` | Research-derived doctrine adoption: peck verification discipline and gem-team agent I/O contract (2 phases) | In Progress |\n129:| 002 | `002-memory-store-and-search/` | Memory store and retrieval hardening: write-safety, index and causal lifecycle, semantic triggers, feedback reducers, memclaw hardening, observability, continuity, vector and BM25 search resilience (14 phases) | In Progress |\n132:| 005 | `005-verification-and-remediation/` | Verify-first program: finding remediation, tri-system deep research, deep-research remediation, residual design units (4 phases) | In Progress |\n","metadata":{"output":"127:| 000 | `000-release-cleanup/` | Outward and governance surface alignment for release: public README, skill docs, feature catalog, manual playbook, MCP/CLI stress, commands, agents, AGENTS.md | In Progress |\n128:| 001 | `001-research-and-doctrine/` | Research-derived doctrine adoption: peck verification discipline and gem-team agent I/O contract (2 phases) | In Progress |\n129:| 002 | `002-memory-store-and-search/` | Memory store and retrieval hardening: write-safety, index and causal lifecycle, semantic triggers, feedback reducers, memclaw hardening, observability, continuity, vector and BM25 search resilience (14 phases) | In Progress |\n132:| 005 | `005-verification-and-remediation/` | Verify-first program: finding remediation, tri-system deep research, deep-research remediation, residual design units (4 phases) | In Progress |\n","exit":0,"description":"Verify F001 still holds","truncated":false},"title":"Verify F001 still holds","time":{"start":1781423297307,"end":1781423297309}},"id":"prt_ec51a5310001SjLVSHka1LxLtx","sessionID":"ses_13aef63ccffel7tpaI1Dzxs3uq","messageID":"msg_ec5199e0c001DY9DYhcSYFM6N6"}}
